:<font size="15">משׁל</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
משׁל / mâshal / maw-shal'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''משׁל'''

# To [[rule]]: - (have, make to have) dominion, governor, X indeed, reign, (bear, cause to, have) rule (-ing, -r), have power.

